description:
Went there yesterday, very very relaxing and great view in eyes; the seats are first come, first serve; there are two sides (different views) on top floor, 39th, if I remember it correctly, you can see the night view of the city; very breath-taking; heart-speeding, as if.

You can totally wear anything you want, it's a drinking bar, not dance bar; chat and drink and enjoy some relaxing time here; 

OMG, i like it, so bitchin'
